        "padding_bottom": 112,
        "kicker": "LATEST TECHNOLOGY 2026",
        "heading": "You Have <span class=\"font-bold italic\">Never</span> Seen A Massage Chair Like This",
        "text": "<p>PHYSIO+® by World of Comfort redefines the massage chair category with dual system rollers featuring six independent mechanisms that work in harmony. Powered by AI BioSensory Intelligence™, PHYSIO+® scans your body's health indicators — heart rate, blood oxygen, microcirculation, and fatigue index — to deliver a fully personalized massage. The innovative walking technology uses a scissor-action mechanism to mimic natural walking motion, stretching the lower back, glutes, hamstrings, and knees. With a self-adaptive flexible SL-track, 2-stage zero gravity, deep tissue arm rollers, heated foot rollers, touchscreen remote, Bluetooth surround sound, wireless phone charging, and intelligent voice control — PHYSIO+® is not just a massage chair; it is your personal wellness clinic at home.</p>"
      }
