          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can multiple family members use PHYSIO+® with personalized settings?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. PHYSIO+®'s AI BioSensory Intelligence™ performs a fresh health scan before each session, automatically tailoring the massage to whichever family member is using the chair. The precision body scan detects each user's unique body shape and adjusts roller positioning accordingly.</p>"
